---
import Container from 'shared/_components/container/index.astro'
---

<Container class="md:flex md:mb-12 md:mt-16 space-y-20 md:space-y-0 justify-between items-stretch gap-10">
	<section class="shadow-md bg-white px-10 py-4">
		<span class="text-[orange] text-7xl block">ƛ</span>
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-light mt-5">Function Oriented</h2>
		<p class="font-light text-md text-gray-500 my-5">
			<strong class="font-bold">Functional, but in the Javascript way.</strong><br />
			Use the best of the Javascript Functional Features.
		</p>
	</section>
	<section class="shadow-md bg-white px-10 py-4">
		<span class="text-[orange] text-7xl font-thin block">🏝</span>
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-light mt-5">Island Architecture</h2>
		<p class="font-light text-md text-gray-500 my-5">
			<strong class="font-bold">Small, focused chunks of interactivity</strong> within static<br /> and server-rendered web pages
		</p>
	</section>
	<section class="shadow-md bg-white px-10 py-4">
		<img class="w-16 inline-block" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/JavaScript-logo.png/600px-JavaScript-logo.png" alt="Javascript Logo" />
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-light mt-5">Ecossystem Compatible</h2>
		<p class="font-light text-md text-gray-500 my-5">
			<strong>Integrate</strong> your Application with <strong class="font-bold">any other <br />
			Javascript Library easily</strong>.
		</p>
	</section>
</Container>
